stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> MenuBrowse: Customer/Staff selects items

    MenuBrowse --> Cart: Add to cart

    Cart --> Held: Hold/Park order
    Held --> Cart: Resume held order

    Cart --> KitchenSent: Send to Kitchen (KOT)
    Cart --> DirectPay: Pay Now

    KitchenSent --> Preparing: Kitchen starts
    Preparing --> Ready: Kitchen completes
    Ready --> Completed: Served/Picked up

    KitchenSent --> CollectPayment: Collect Payment later
    CollectPayment --> Paid: Payment received

    DirectPay --> Paid: Transaction logged
    Paid --> Completed: Order finalized

    Cart --> EditMode: Add items to existing order
    EditMode --> KitchenSent: Append new items

    Completed --> [*]

    note right of Held
        Stored in localStorage
        Key: qs-held-orders
    end note

    note right of KitchenSent
        Creates kitchen_order record
        Triggers inventory deduction
        payment_status: pending
    end note

    note right of Paid
        pos_transactions record created
        Supports: Cash, UPI, Card, NC
    end note

    state Cart {
        [*] --> ItemsAdded
        ItemsAdded --> DiscountApplied: Apply coupon/loyalty
        ItemsAdded --> CustomerLinked: Link CRM customer
    }
